ression-boost-stress-calming-gut-bacteria.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 01:31:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/glp-1-drugs-reduce-depression-boost-stress-calming-gut-bacteria</guid></item><item><title>你的大脑是一根天线——重写现实的诺贝尔奖获奖理论</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/your-brain-is-an-antenna-the-nobel-prize-winning-theory-that-rewrites-reality</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 01:16:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/your-brain-is-an-antenna-the-nobel-prize-winning-theory-that-rewrites-reality</guid></item><item><title>生命如何学会思考：智力的完整历史</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-life-learned-to-think-the-complete-history-of-intelligence</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 01:01:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-life-learned-to-think-the-complete-history-of-intelligence</guid></item><item><title>过度参数化令人费解的成功：彩票还是逃生维度？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-puzzling-success-of-overparameterization-lottery-tickets-or-escape-dimensions</link><description>彩票和彩票经常被用作教学类比来解释过度参数化神经网络的成功：“较大的网络之所以成功，是因为它们更有可能包含一个初始化良好的子网络，可以独立学习任务，就像购买更多彩票会增加中彩票的机会一样。” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-puzzling-success-of-overparameterization-lottery-tickets-or-escape-dimensions.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 00:46:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-puzzling-success-of-overparameterization-lottery-tickets-or-escape-dimensions</guid></item><item><title>大黄蜂自发解决问题</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/spontaneous-problem-solving-in-bumble-bees</link><description>在没有明确训练的情况下使用新颖的解决方案解决问题通常被认为是认知灵活性的标志。我们调查了